 "lrc": "[00:00.00]Title: Move Over (Minimal Groove Mix)\n[00:00.00]Somebody said the floor already had a king?\n[00:12.43]Ha.\n[00:12.52]Move over.\n[00:12.69]Move over\n[00:12.87]We got heat in the room\n[00:15.78]Move over\n[00:16.48]Summer came through smooth\n[00:18.72]Don’t talk too much\n[00:20.48]Just let that bassline hit\n[00:22.08]This summer different\n[00:24.08]You can tell by the drip\n[00:26.56](Yeah)\n[00:27.76]Let it ride\n[00:30.40]Bassline talking\n[00:34.56](shh, just listen)\n[00:36.64]Slow steps, low lights\n[00:38.16](so smooth)\n[00:39.28]Keep it simple\n[00:40.48]Just move\n[00:41.44]Mmm.\n[00:42.80]That’s enough.\n[00:46.08]Let it breathe.\n[00:47.04]Move over\n[00:50.40]We got heat in the room\n[00:52.96]Move over\n[00:54.32]Summer came through smooth\n[00:56.56]Don’t talk too much\n[00:58.00]Just let that bassline hit\n[00:59.84]This summer different\n[01:01.92]You can tell by the drip\n[01:05.92]Move.\n[01:06.88]Move.\n[01:07.20]Move over.\n[01:10.72]Move.\n[01:10.72]Move.\n[01:11.36]Move over.\n[01:11.52]You feel that?\n[01:19.28]Oh, we do.\n[01:21.28]Turn it up.\n[01:22.16]Slide it through.\n[01:23.12]Soft steps.\n[01:27.12]Deep bass.\n[01:29.20](mmm, yeah, right there)\n[01:34.32]Don’t rush it.\n[01:35.28]Don’t force it.\n[01:38.08]Just catch it.\n[01:39.28]Move over\n[01:40.40]We got heat in the room\n[01:42.10]Move over\n[01:42.11]Summer came through smooth\n[01:42.14]Don’t talk too much\n[01:42.16]Just let that bassline hit\n[01:42.20]This summer different\n[01:42.22]You can tell by the drip\n[01:42.96]Kick.\n[01:43.20]Clap.\n[01:43.20]Bass.\n[01:43.28]Breathe.\n[01:43.68]Kick.\n[01:46.00]Clap.\n[01:46.83]Bass.\n[01:47.04]Breathe.\n[01:47.25]Somebody said the floor had a king?\n[02:09.60]Cute.\n[02:09.68]Move over\n[02:14.00]We got heat in the room\n[02:17.84]Move over\n[02:19.28]Summer came through smooth\n[02:21.52]Don’t talk too much\n[02:22.96]Just let that bassline hit\n[02:24.88]This summer different\n[02:26.96]You can tell by the drip\n[02:30.32]Move.\n[02:32.24]Move.\n[02:32.24]Move over.\n[02:34.32]This summer different.\n[02:36.00]Move.\n[02:38.56]Move.\n[02:38.80]Move over.\n"
